data.description: This charming home has been freshly painted and offers a perfect balance of functionality and comfort.  The cozy antique fireplace adds warmth and character in the second living area, and the kitchen is sure to fit your needs.  It is Located in a quiet cul-de-sac within WALKING distance to Jim Ned High and Middle School and is very close to Lowe's grocery store and all other small-town amenities. If you are ready to get away from the hustle and bustle of the big city but still be close to amenities, then this is the home for you! It's ready for a new family and your personal touch Must see in person! (Home has undergone virtual staging)
